name: ACEiForHFrEF
title: ACEi for HFrEF
purpose: (Clinical Focus: ACE inhibitors which have HFrEF as approved indication, per Clinical Pharmacology (https://www.clinicalkey.com/pharmacology/resources/overviews?id=1216635#TherapeuticUse).),(Data Element Scope: RxCUIs fitting exclusion and inclusion criteria.),(Inclusion Criteria: Medications containing captopril, enalapril, fosinopril, lisinopril, quinapril, ramapril, and trandalopril, including combination medications.),(Exclusion Criteria: Non-prescribable medicaions, and medications containing benazepril, perindopril, or moexepril.)
